#    SAMTOOLS: 	http://samtools.sourceforge.net/
#
# ChIP-seq (HOMER)
#
#    FASTQC: 	http://www.bioinformatics.babraham.ac.uk/projects/fastqc/
#    HOMER: 	http://homer.salk.edu/homer/ngs/index.html
